text.section:
The secretary shall promulgate administrative regulations to accommodate the specific circumstances of home-based microprocessors. In order to protect public health while encouraging the marketing of home-processed foods, the administrative regulations shall include, at a minimum, standards for:
Installation, design, location, and maintenance of toilet rooms;
Installation and maintenance of hand-washing facilities;
Manual and mechanical cleaning and sanitizing processes;
Installation and location of equipment;
Construction and covering of floors; and
Construction, materials, and maintenance of walls and ceilings.
